+modal('bip-ntier', "N-Tier Supply Chain Map")
  p Built an interactive multi-tier supply chain network visualisation.
  p The graph rendered supplier relationships across multiple tiers using a canvas-based engine with a radial layout computed in a Web Worker.
  p Features included node clustering, tier-based color coding, zoom/pan controls, a supplier side panel with risk and insight data, and portfolio-based filtering.
  p The visualisation handled graphs with hundreds of nodes while maintaining interactive frame rates.
